{"tid":1990930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"十萬火急 召集 Deadline Figher 香港人！要人啊！","createTime":"2020-04-27T05:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T09:13:57.000Z","uid":167548,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c38f319321da727feb4128d76cdcc387cb7198a8","tid":1990930,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">選民登記最後一星期！五一黃金週！最後衝刺！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔該五一黃金週商店可以幫手印定一些<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>選民登記表格</strong></span>比食客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中老一輩見此POST唔識得用網上登記/郵寄, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請到各區搵區議員幫手</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qENcvdq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqENcvdq.jpg&h=083ae4fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後生未必黃, 中老一輩有心好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxngTr2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxngTr2.jpg&h=9a20fa7b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n梁凱晴：18至30歲有30萬人未登記做選民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcHXcYF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcHXcYF.png&h=163b9dca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1edfe87ed94f6758cb29e1e5327d86b32bf96c3f","tid":1990930,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>片尾最後提到，香港人剩下嘅空間已經越來越窄、權利越來越少，所以每一個新選民就係香港嘅新希望，呼籲大家唔好令自己後悔。YouTube片段： <a href=\"https://youtu.be/-IU2V_UXK54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-IU2V_UXK54&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=702c8906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-IU2V_UXK54</a><br />\n<br />\n今年嘅選民登記截止日期係下個月嘅2號，市民需要喺嗰日或之前遞交選民登記申請，先可以喺今年第七屆立法會選舉投票，而因應部份設施受武漢肺炎影響關閉，選舉事務處提醒市民如果經郵寄遞交申請，就要盡早寄出，而選舉事務處喺九龍灣國際展貿中心嘅辦事處，亦會喺截止日辦公到晚上11時59分，以便接收申請表；如已登記嘅選民若果收到選舉事務處嘅查詢信件，亦要喺5月2日或之前回覆以保留選民登記。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n● 選民登記截止：5月2日<br />\n● 登記表格： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3eO2sFD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3eO2sFD&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=abffdda6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3eO2sFD</a><br />\n● 登記方法<br />\n將選民登記表格連同住址證明（更改住址亦適用）送交選舉事務處，包括：<br />\n1. 郵寄到九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n2. 或傳真至2891 1180<br />\n3. 或掃描表格後電郵至form@reo.gov.hk<br />\n4. 或掃描表格後上載至選舉事務處電子表格上載平台 <a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=a352bdb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n詳情可瀏覽： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KCjVTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KCjVTA&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=f3c2c85f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KCjVTA</a><br />\n<br />\n●立法會選舉投票日：9月6日<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2F4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4I26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=7623eb75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200427%2F4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY%2F&h=a4a184e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200427/4FO32M2X5Z67EHBJS5XMCE27HY/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"baee6cf1d7e388c18cd3fc574bc4c81fdc9d